$(document).ready(()=>{let e=$(".articles");$("#categories").on("change",function(){$(".preload").show(),setTimeout(function(){$(".preload").hide()},1e3),e.text("");const t=$("#categories option:selected").val();$.ajax({url:`https://api.nytimes.com/svc/topstories/v2/${t}.json?api-key=cMfA0NO0S102DbxZsVap17SSVyu0hWxT`}).done(function(t){$(".main-header, .logo").addClass("loaded");let s=0;for(let a=0;a<t.results.length;a++)if(t.results[a].multimedia.length>=5&&s<12){s+=1;let l=t.results[a].multimedia[4].url,i=t.results[a].abstract,n=`<li class='article'>\n          <a href=${t.results[a].url} alt='url' target='_blank'><img src=${l}></a>\n          <p class='description'>${i}</p>\n          </li>`;e.append(n)}}).fail(()=>{e.append("<p>Sorry, something went wrong</p>")})})});